The paper focuses on developing algorithms for secure mobile edge computing in IoT, which involves online learning and security against jamming attacks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also deals with distributed computing and communication, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
